# Pygame Projects

This repository contains a collection of simple and fun projects created using the Pygame library. Each project is a standalone game or interactive application showcasing different aspects of Pygame and game development concepts.

## Installation

To run the projects, make sure you have Python and Pygame installed on your system. If you don't have Pygame, you can install it using pip:

```
pip install pygame
```

## How to Run

Navigate to the project folder and run the main Python script:

```
cd Project1
python main.py
```

Have fun exploring the games and applications!

